      <title>即使在沙特阿拉伯，可再生能源也比化石燃料便宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/even-in-saudi-arabia-renewable-power-is-cheaper-than-fossil-fuels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯签署了从两个比天然气发电厂便宜的大型风电场购买电力的协议，其目标是迅速过渡到电网中更大份额的可再生能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/even-in-saudi-arabia-renewable-power-is-cheaper-than-fossil-fuels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 07:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
